{"tid":2075124,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"竹篙灣檢疫中心工程不達標 政府監工唔收貨遭工人圍毆","createTime":"2020-06-22T15:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T15:25:05.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb74da2d4f2c0f7ba94c7ce1d49a8bf6d87fbbc9","tid":2075124,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"被譽為「港版火神山」的竹篙灣檢疫中心，其中一幅工地發生集體圍毆事件。消息稱，一名土木工程拓展署監工，上周六（20日）晚上在竹篙灣工地檢視一個工程，發現有工序不符合標準，拒絕簽收滿意紙。豈料翌日（21日）早上他在工地內竟遭一批工人圍毆，事後頭部及手部受傷，送醫治理，警方接報經調查拘捕涉案工人帶署調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，昨日（21日）接獲一名36歲姓郭男子報案，指他早上約9時於大嶼山竹篙灣一地盤內因工作表現問題與3名同事爭執，其間被同事以手襲擊，一部手提電話被毀壞。該名36歲報案人報稱頭及手受傷，自行前往北大嶼山醫院治理後向警方報案。警方經初步調查，昨日下午返回案發地盤拘捕3名男子，年齡介乎33至36歲，涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害及刑事毀壞。3名被捕人現已被保釋候查，案件交由大嶼警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200622/R4DVJSEPGLI5TS5U5W2U6CYZ2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200622%2FR4DVJSEPGLI5TS5U5W2U6CYZ2A%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7om5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=7e9784e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200622%2FR4DVJSEPGLI5TS5U5W2U6CYZ2A%2F&h=17810e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200622/R4DVJSEPGLI5TS5U5W2U6CYZ2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/orcsCoBoeHyk5KUtk6x1npuAWXg=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/OISIXGF53NHOQB66PWLLLX2IKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2ForcsCoBoeHyk5KUtk6x1npuAWXg%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FOISIXGF53NHOQB66PWLLLX2IKU.jpg&h=fce79777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/SNJvbnsEXAwOWawBGPSo1VRfGMc=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/PMP4USJDGROJ7Z4M66427EQBEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2FSNJvbnsEXAwOWawBGPSo1VRfGMc%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FPMP4USJDGROJ7Z4M66427EQBEQ.jpg&h=3923e59b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}